  <brief_title>Hamstrings Autograft Versus Tibialis Allograft for Reconstruction of Anterior Cruciate Ligament</brief_title>
  <official_title>Hamstrings Autograft Versus Tibialis Allograft for Reconstruction of Anterior Cruciate Ligament: Randomized Clinical Trial With 2 Year Follow-up</official_title>
